这本书为理解印度教与冈仁波齐的关系提供了社会学视角。`,
    fullQuoteEn: `"Hinduism: Religion and Society" is a comprehensive work introducing Hinduism's belief system and social functions. It provides detailed elaboration on Kailasa's position within Hinduism:

